1. *Čekaju* se rezultati u petak. (They are awaiting the results on Friday.)

2. Oni su *čekali* dugo da dobiju vesti. (They had been waiting a long time to receive the news.)

3. *Čeka* se da se povežu sa drugom stranom. (They are waiting to connect with the other side.)

4. *Čekajući*, on je počeo da čita knjigu. (While waiting, he started to read a book.)

5. *Čeka* se da se otvori vrata. (They are waiting for the doors to open.)